---
import { useTranslations } from '@/i18n';

const t = useTranslations('es');
---

<section class="py-32 px-6">
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
    <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold text-primary mb-12">
      {t.home.manifesto.title}
    </h2>
    <div class="prose prose-lg text-secondary space-y-6">
      <p>
        Ponto Socorro es un espacio sagrado donde la fe se vive a través de la música y la comunidad. 
        Founded in the tradition of Santo Daime, our community gathers to sing hymns that connect 
        us with the divine and with each other.
      </p>
      <p>
        Los himnos que compartimos son mensajes de amor, luz y esperanza. Cada canto carrying 
        the wisdom of generations of seekers who have walked this path before us. Through music, 
        we find a direct connection to the spiritual realm.
      </p>
      <p>
        Our mission is to preserve and share this rich musical heritage, making these sacred 
        songs accessible to all who seek their light. In our community, every voice matters 
        and every heart is welcome.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
